'''周庭'''（{{lang-en|Agnes Chow Ting}}；{{bd|1996年|12月3日||catIdx=Z周}}），[[香港|香港]][[民主派_(香港)|民主派]][[政治人物|政治人物]]，[[學民思潮|學民思潮]]前發言人，[[香港眾志|香港眾志]]創黨成員兼前常委、前副秘書長，曾任前[[香港立法會議員|香港立法會議員]][[區諾軒|區諾軒]]助理<ref>{{cite news |title=【Emily】議助不再 之鋒周庭失業 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191218/s00002/1576606139201/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E8%AD%B0%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D-%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD |work=明報 |date=2019-12-18 |accessdate=2020-12-07 |archive-date=2019-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218141805/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191218/s00002/1576606139201/%e3%80%90emily%e3%80%91%e8%ad%b0%e5%8a%a9%e4%b8%8d%e5%86%8d-%e4%b9%8b%e9%8b%92%e5%91%a8%e5%ba%ad%e5%a4%b1%e6%a5%ad |dead-url=no }}</ref>。被稱「學民女神」<ref name=":3">{{cite web|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AD%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E-%E8%A9%A6%E5%81%9A%E5%8D%B7-%E8%A2%AB%E8%A9%95%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89-220213393.html|title=「學民女神」試做卷 被評中等|work=星島日報|date=2013-04-11|accessdate=2015-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223190247/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AD%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E-%E8%A9%A6%E5%81%9A%E5%8D%B7-%E8%A2%AB%E8%A9%95%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89-220213393.html|archive-date=2015-12-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>或「學運女神」<ref>{{Cite web|title=香港「學運女神」周庭出獄了！ 民眾冒雨集結高呼「加油」|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3567382|author=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|date=2021-06-12|accessdate=2021-06-20|publisher=[[自由時報|自由時報]]|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2021-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621185902/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3567382|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="HKBU">{{Cite web|title=香港學運女神周庭FB發布甜美學士照 宣告：「我大學畢業啦」|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201119/NXMCMYUED5G7XEAESAX4GPTSVI/|date=2020-11-19|accessdate=2021-06-20|publisher=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果新聞網]]|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120011854/https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201119/NXMCMYUED5G7XEAESAX4GPTSVI/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，更被[[日本|日本]]傳媒多番稱為「民主女神」<ref name="DW"></ref>和「聖女貞德」<ref name="JA"></ref>。周庭本為[[英國公民|英國公民]]，是家人在她年幼時為她申請的，但她從未在[[英國|英國]]定居<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/140113/政壇諸事町-周庭為選戰形象大變身-正辦理放棄英籍手續|title=【政壇諸事町】周庭為選戰形象大變身　正辦理放棄英籍手續|date=2017-12-09|work=香港01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115172624/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/140113/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E7%82%BA%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%8A%E8%BA%AB-%E6%AD%A3%E8%BE%A6%E7%90%86%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E8%8B%B1%E7%B1%8D%E6%89%8B%E7%BA%8C|archive-date=2019-11-15|deadurl=no|access-date=2020-07-19}}</ref>。

她先後就讀[[嘉諾撒聖家學校|嘉諾撒聖家學校]]及[[嘉諾撒聖家書院|嘉諾撒聖家書院]]<ref name=":4">{{cite news |title=周庭：我是懷著怎樣的心情？ |url=https://www.hkcnews.com/article/19086/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97-%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-19088/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E6%87%B7%E8%91%97%E6%80%8E%E6%A8%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%83%E6%83%85%EF%BC%9F |work=眾新聞 |date=2019-03-14 |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901021125/https://www.hkcnews.com/article/19086/%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597-%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2582%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-19088/%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2587%25B7%25E8%2591%2597%25E6%2580%258E%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2583%2585%25EF%25BC%259F |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":5">{{cite news |title=【短片．Emily Online】周庭游泳短片　原非支持區諾軒 (19:39) |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20180304/s00001/1520162672995/%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-emily-online%E3%80%91%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E5%8E%9F%E9%9D%9E%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8D%80%E8%AB%BE%E8%BB%92 |work=明報 |date=2018-03-04 |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901021126/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E/article/20180304/s00001/1520162672995/%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-emily-online%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%258E%259F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25BB%2592 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在15歲就讀中四期間加入成為學民思潮成員。到2014年升讀[[香港浸會大學|香港浸會大學]]社會科學學士<ref name=":6">{{cite news |title=聯招放榜黃之鋒有大學收　周庭亦獲浸大取錄 |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20140808/bkn-20140808161312408-0808_00822_001.html |work=on.cc. |date=2014-08-08 |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901015230/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20140808/bkn-20140808161312408-0808_00822_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":7">{{cite news |title=學民3準大學生 首務大罷課 |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223154316/http://life.mingpao.com/htm/hkdse/cfm/news3.cfm?File=20140809%2Fnews%2Fgba2.txt |work=明報 |date=2014-08-09}}</ref>。同年10月，她在[[雨傘革命|雨傘革命]]期間辭任學民思潮發言人<ref name=":8">{{cite news |title=難抵壓力　周庭辭任學民發言人 |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20141012/18897534 |work=蘋果日報 |date=2014-10-12 |accessdate=2015-12-23 |archive-date=2016-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421110457/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20141012/18897534 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。到2016年與[[香港專上學生聯會|香港專上學生聯會]]前秘書長羅冠聰、學民思潮前召集人黃之鋒創立新政黨香港眾志<ref name=":9">{{cite news |title=【學民組黨】羅冠聰公布黨名為「香港眾志」　英文「Demosisto」意指人民團結自立 (21:11) |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20160406/s00001/1459947094244/%e3%80%90%e5%ad%b8%e6%b0%91%e7%b5%84%e9%bb%a8%e3%80%91%e7%be%85%e5%86%a0%e8%81%b0%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%83%e9%bb%a8%e5%90%8d%e7%82%ba%e3%80%8c%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%9c%be%e5%bf%97%e3%80%8d-%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%e3%80%8cdemosisto%e3%80%8d%e6%84%8f%e6%8c%87%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%9c%98%e7%b5%90%e8%87%aa%e7%ab%8b |work=明報 |date=2016-04-06 |accessdate=2019-08-31 |archive-date=2021-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623012104/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20160406/s00001/1459947094244/%e3%80%90%e5%ad%b8%e6%b0%91%e7%b5%84%e9%bb%a8%e3%80%91%e7%be%85%e5%86%a0%e8%81%b0%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%83%e9%bb%a8%e5%90%8d%e7%82%ba%e3%80%8c%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%9c%be%e5%bf%97%e3%80%8d-%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%e3%80%8cdemosisto%e3%80%8d%e6%84%8f%e6%8c%87%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%9c%98%e7%b5%90%e8%87%aa%e7%ab%8b |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2018年1月13日，周庭於社交媒體上宣佈參選[[2018年3月香港立法會補選|2018立法會香港島區補選]]，為此放棄英國公民身份以便符合參選條件<ref>{{cite news |title=周庭：棄英籍參選非大犧牲 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20171205/s00002/1512410959347/%e5%91%a8%e5%ba%ad-%e6%a3%84%e8%8b%b1%e7%b1%8d%e5%8f%83%e9%81%b8%e9%9d%9e%e5%a4%a7%e7%8a%a7%e7%89%b2 |work=明報 |date=2017-12-05 |accessdate=2020-12-07 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308233802/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20171205/s00002/1512410959347/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD-%E6%A3%84%E8%8B%B1%E7%B1%8D%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E9%9D%9E%E5%A4%A7%E7%8A%A7%E7%89%B2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於18日遞交提名表格參與補選並已簽署選舉確認書。然而周庭仍然遭到選舉主任[[鄧如欣|鄧如欣]]剝奪參選資格。

2020年6月30日，周庭、[[黃之鋒|黃之鋒]]、[[羅冠聰|羅冠聰]]及[[敖卓軒|敖卓軒]]先後在社交平台上宣佈退出香港眾志。同日下午，香港眾志認為組織運作將難以持續，宣佈即日起解散及停止一切會務<ref>{{cite news |title=【國安法】香港眾志宣佈解散 稱難以持續運作 |url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1808026/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E8%A7%A3%E6%95%A3-%E7%A8%B1%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C |work=頭條日報 |date=2020-06-30 |accessdate=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210110619/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1808026/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E8%A7%A3%E6%95%A3-%E7%A8%B1%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在8月10日，周庭與[[壹傳媒|壹傳媒]]集團創辦人[[黎智英|黎智英]]等多名人士，遭到[[香港警察|香港警察]]以[[港版國安法|港版國安法]]中的罪名進行[[周庭被香港警察國安處拘捕事件|大搜捕]]<ref name=":10">{{cite news |title=警拘黎智英、周庭等六人　涉運作及資助組織促外國制裁 |url=https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=401248 |work=NOW新聞 |date=2020-08-10 |accessdate=2020-08-10 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922160504/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=401248 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年12月2日，周庭於[[西九龍裁判法院|西九龍裁判法院]]承認在2019年6月21日[[2019年6月21日香港反對逃犯條例修訂草案圍堵行動|反送中包圍警察總部]]案中，參與及煽惑他人參與非法集會，被[[裁判官|裁判官]]王詩麗判刑入獄10個月<ref>{{cite news |title=黃之鋒、周庭、林朗彥「621包圍警總」遭判刑7至13.5個月，支持者：當局目的是殺雞儆猴 |url=https://www.twreporter.org/a/hong-kong-joshua-wong-chow-ting-ivan-lam-jailed |agency=報導者 THE REPORTER |date=2020-12-02 |accessdate=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202115259/https://www.twreporter.org/a/hong-kong-joshua-wong-chow-ting-ivan-lam-jailed |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於翌年6月12日刑滿出獄<ref>{{cite web |title=周庭刑滿出獄　遭大批傳媒包圍　未有發言登上私家車離開 |url=https://www.hk01.com/政情/637291/周庭刑滿出獄-遭大批傳媒包圍-未有發言登上私家車離開 |website=香港01 |accessdate=2021-06-12 |date=2021-06-12 |archive-date=2021-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612134906/https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/637291/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E5%88%91%E6%BB%BF%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-%E9%81%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E7%99%BB%E4%B8%8A%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

