-29 |accessdate=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511020933/https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200429/7EA336Q3H6DFVRK7MTQ623L7C4/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

