|work=周庭FaceBook專頁|date=2018-01-13}}</ref>。香港眾志亦公佈了選舉口號為「結伴同行 捲土重來」，並獲[[李柱銘|李柱銘]]、[[梁家傑|梁家傑]]、[[吳靄儀|吳靄儀]]、[[楊岳橋|楊岳橋]]、[[陳志全|陳志全]]、[[朱凱廸|朱凱廸]]及[[許智峯|許智峯]]站台發言支持<ref name="#1">{{Cite web |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E5%87%BA%E6%88%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E6%9D%8E%E6%9F%B1%E9%8A%98%E5%90%B3%E9%9D%84%E5%84%80%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E7%AD%89%E7%AB%99%E5%8F%B0%E9%80%A0%E5%8B%A2/ |title=周庭正式宣佈出戰港島補選　李柱銘吳靄儀朱凱廸等站台造勢 |access-date=2019-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609004604/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E5%87%BA%E6%88%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E6%9D%8E%E6%9F%B1%E9%8A%98%E5%90%B3%E9%9D%84%E5%84%80%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E7%AD%89%E7%AB%99%E5%8F%B0%E9%80%A0%E5%8B%A2/ |archive-date=2019-06-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

